body.p:
For example, to specify that all bookmarks for the first three levels are opened (expanded)
      in the initial state,
      use:*[class~="topic/topic"] > *[class~="topic/title"],
*[class~="topic/topic"] *[class~="topic/topic"] > *[class~="topic/title"],
*[class~="topic/topic"] *[class~="topic/topic"] *[class~="topic/topic"] > *[class~="topic/title"] {
     bookmark-state:open;
}
